{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "1.760", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "1.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "11.720", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine sehr geehrten Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "11.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.120", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Schulz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.880", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie machen es sich reichlich einfach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "17.120", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Ihnen die Debatte so wichtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "17.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.760", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn die Arbeitspl\u00e4tze und die Perspektiven f\u00fcr die Siemens-Werke Ihnen so wichtig sind und Sie die amtierende Wirtschaftsministerin loben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.160", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "frage ich Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.960", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo ist eigentlich Ihre amtierende Wirtschaftsministerin? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.160", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann sie nicht sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.360", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie machen es sich auch aus einem anderen Grund sehr einfach. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.000", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Gegensatz zu Ihnen glauben wir nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der Deutsche Bundestag direkt \u00fcber Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in der Privatwirtschaft entscheidet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.560", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber das, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.240", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie mitverantworten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.720", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Regierungspolitik unter Schwarz-Rot,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.440", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hat mit dazu gef\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.720", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass kein Unternehmen in Deutschland im Moment bereit ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.680", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in konventionelle Kraftwerkskapazit\u00e4ten und in Versorgungssicherheit zu investieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.920", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das sollten Sie zur Kenntnis nehmen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.920", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Schulz."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.040", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Freie Demokraten billigen Unternehmen zu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.040", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unternehmerische Entscheidungen zu treffen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um wettbewerbsf\u00e4hig zu bleiben; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.360", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist so."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.240", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich sage auch: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.680", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Siemens ist kein kleiner Mittelst\u00e4ndler, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.240", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Siemens steht finanziell auch nicht mit dem R\u00fccken zur Wand."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.280", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Siemens hat deshalb eine Verantwortung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.480", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nur f\u00fcr die eigene Aktie und die eigene Dividende, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.840", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch f\u00fcr Mitarbeiter und Standorte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.400", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aus diesem Grund muss ich schon hinterfragen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.400", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum begr\u00fcndet wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.440", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die angeblich zu hohen Kosten gerade an den Standorten im Osten\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.200", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Erfurt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.320", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Leipzig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.040", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in G\u00f6rlitz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.960", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Berlin\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.600", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "entscheidend daf\u00fcr sein sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.080", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Werke zu schlie\u00dfen oder Produktionen zu verlagern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "G\u00fcnstige Produktionskosten sind doch eher im Osten zu finden und nirgendwo anders. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "135.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb kann ich die Siemens-Entscheidung nicht nachvollziehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "135.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.360", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In meinem Heimatbundesland, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "138.400", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in der Lausitz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "138.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00e4mpfen die Menschen heute noch mit den Auswirkungen des Strukturwandels, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.360", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der durch die Wende entstanden ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "147.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie waren gerade aus dem Gr\u00f6bsten heraus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "147.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "149.200", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es hat Hoffnung gegeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "149.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann k\u00fcndigte Bombardier an, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Mitarbeiterzahl in den Werken zu verringern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Damoklesschwert Kohle schwebt \u00fcber der Region, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was f\u00fcr die Wertsch\u00f6pfung eine immense Bedeutung hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und jetzt Siemens! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.240", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich kann den Frust der Menschen in der Region verstehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.880", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was den Standort G\u00f6rlitz angeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.680", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "plant Siemens ja keinen sofortigen Ausstieg. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.640", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angesichts der langen Perspektive frage ich mich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum kann ein so gro\u00dfer Konzern, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "einer von Deutschlands f\u00fchrenden Technologiekonzernen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.800", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es sich nicht leisten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.360", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "neue Produkte zu entwickeln und \u00fcber Alternativen nachzudenken? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.520", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn man die Produktion schon konzentriert und \u00fcber die Aufgabe von Standorten nachdenkt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.400", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann kann man vielleicht auch dar\u00fcber nachdenken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.280", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "neue Produkte in G\u00f6rlitz und anderswo herstellen zu lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich kann nur hoffen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.800", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das sage ich im Namen der Menschen in der Lausitz\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.480", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das Siemens-Management noch einmal \u00fcber seine Entscheidung nachdenkt und den Standorten eine Perspektive gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.240", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.560", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist ein Appell der Politik. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.320", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Gegensatz zu Ihnen gaukle ich den Menschen nicht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.000", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir hier im Bundestag \u00fcber die Arbeitspl\u00e4tze entscheiden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.440", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich setze darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das letzte Wort noch nicht gesprochen ist und die Standorte eine Perspektive bekommen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.040", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.960", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr die Fraktion Die Linke hat Klaus Ernst das Wort."
   ]
  }
 ]
}